Bottom Navigation Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides bottom navigation bar system for mobile applications.
Implements fixed bottom navigation with multiple destinations, icon/text labels,
and navigation switching optimized for mobile bottom navigation patterns.

Key Features:
- Fixed bottom navigation bar
- Multiple navigation destinations
- Icon and text label combinations
- Badge notifications
- Active/inactive state styling
- Smooth navigation transitions
- Accessibility navigation support
- Custom bottom bar styling
- Overflow handling for many items
- Integration with view controllers
- Platform-specific bottom nav styles
- Animation and selection feedback

Provides complete bottom navigation system for building mobile applications
with persistent bottom navigation and proper destination switching.
